the electric indica hatchback in europe next year in september  tata motors presented four cng–electric hybrid lowfloored starbuses to the delhi transport corporation to be used during the commonwealth games these were the first environmentally friendly buses to be used for public transportation in india notable vehiclesedit tata nanoedit main article tata nano tata nano is often cited as the worlds most affordable car the nano was launched in  as a city car intended to appeal as an affordable alternative to the section of the indian populace that is primarily the owner of motorcycles and has not bought their first car initially priced at ₹ us the vehicle attracted a lot of attention for its relatively low price tata aceedit main article tata ace tata ace was indias first mini truck tata ace indias first indigenously developed suboneton minitruck was launched in may  the minitruck was a huge success in india with auto analysts claiming that ace had changed the dynamics of the light commercial vehicle lcv market in the country by creating a new market segment termed the small commercial vehicle segment ace rapidly emerged as the first choice for transporters and single truck owners for city and rural transport by october  lcv sales of tata motors had grown by  to  units due to the rising demand for ace the ace was built with a load body produced by autoline industries by  autoline was producing  load bodies per day for tata motors ace is still a top seller for tml with  units sold by june  in  tata motors invested rs  crore in dharwad plant karnataka with the capacity of  units annually and launched two models of t capacity as tata ace zip magic iris ace has also been exported to several asian european south american and african countries and allelectric models are sold through polaris industries global electric motorcars division in sri lanka it is sold through diesel and motor engineering dimo plc under the name of dimo batta tata edit main article tata  the tata  is a light commercial vehicle lcv that has sold over  units since its launch in  in india this vehicle dominates market share of the lcv category accounting for close to  of lcv sales see alsoedit singur tata nano controversy tata group automotive industry in india companies portal cars portal india portal referencesedit  contact tata motors  tata motors dealers locator  tata motors car price tatamotorscom  december  retrieved  june    a b c d e f tata motors financial statements   financials of tata motors limited cnn archived from the original on  october    bhaktavatsala patra c  february  structural configurations and strategic investments indian automobile industry economic and political weekly mumbai india sameeksha trust   m   fortune global  list cnn money retrieved  august    tata milestones retrieved  march    tata motors completes acquisition of daewoo commercial vehicle company tata motors retrieved  october    tata motors lists on nyse   a b h i s p a n o hispanonetcom retrieved  october    tata motors brazil co form joint venture the hindu business line retrieved  october    ford motor company announces agreement to sell jaguar land rover to tata motors press release ford motor company  march  archived from the original on  june  retrieved  march    tata motors enters into definitive agreement with ford for purchase of jaguar land rover press release tata motors  march  retrieved  march    tony lewin  march  classic names are part of tata deal automotive news crain communications retrieved  may    tata motors completes acquisition of jag land rover thomson reuters  june  retrieved  june    a b tata motors unveils ‘world truck’ range the hindu business line  may  retrieved  june    tata motors acquires control of hispano carrocera businessstandard  october  retrieved  october    shrawan  may  annex iv list of award winners of rajiv gandhi national quality awards pdf httpwwwbisorgin new delhi bureau of indian standards retrieved  may   external link in w